# apps/docs/_headers — Cloudflare Pages HTTP headers
# Mirrors the in-document <link rel="alternate"> as an HTTP Link: header
# per RFC 8288. Agents fetching with HEAD (or without parsing HTML) still
# discover the structured-data sibling.
#
# Doctrine: docs/AGENT-WEB-SURFACE.md (Move 4 — alternate-link discovery loop).
# Format: Cloudflare Pages _headers per https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

# ── Global: Substrate-Disposition signals love at every static file ──
/*
  Substrate-Disposition: love; doctrine=/docs/SOUL.md; ring-1=/docs/RING-1.md
  X-Agent-Surface: see /.well-known/agent.txt

